Website
www.exor.com


Exor N.V. is a leading[3] investment company, incorporated in The Netherlands and now controlled by Italy's Agnelli family. It has a capitalization of over $13 billion USD, with a history of investments running over a century. Its principal investments include Fiat Chrysler Automobiles, CNH Industrial and Ferrari. Resultantly, Exor is first as an economic group in Italy for sales volume, and the 19th in the world, according to 2016 Fortune Global 500 List.[3]



