Exor N.V. Key Developments

Exor Hldg NV will Change its Name to Exor NV
May 22 17
Effective May 23, 2017, Exor Hldg NV will change its name to Exor NV.


Exor N.V. Announces Consolidated Earnings Results for the Year Ended December 31, 2016
Apr 5 17
Exor N.V. announced consolidated earnings results for the year ended December 31, 2016. For the full year, the company reported Profit was EUR 588.6 million against profit of EUR 222.4 million a year ago. Profit attributable to shareholders was EUR 588.6 million against profit attributable to shareholders of EUR 744.5 million a year ago. The negative change of EUR 155.9 million can be ascribed to lower gains on the disposal of investments an increase in income taxes and other taxes and duties.


Exor N.V. to Report Fiscal Year 2016 Results on Apr 05, 2017
Feb 1 17
Exor N.V. announced that they will report fiscal year 2016 results on Apr 05, 2017


